would show to

00:20:44.250 --> 00:20:49.380
manufacture curves where none had existed
before.

00:20:49.380 --> 00:20:53.320
One of them ran to fetch Lola's nephew, who
ran the photography

00:20:53.320 --> 00:20:58.430
business next door, while the others demonstrated
facial expressions

00:20:58.430 --> 00:21:03.040
guaranteed to delight mothers-in-law, causing
me to burst into

00:21:03.040 --> 00:21:07.070
laughter, something I never did in the presence
of strangers.

00:21:07.070 --> 00:21:13.450
But they were no longer strangers.
They had charmed me with their daring jokes,

00:21:13.450 --> 00:21:17.600
their code words for
particular beauty procedures, their gallant

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:23.120
laughter in the face of the
drudgery that I guessed awaited them once

00:21:23.120 --> 00:21:26.510
they stepped out of the
magical perimeter of Lola's salon.

00:21:26.510 --> 00:21:33.760
The next morning, when my mother armed me
with a parasol to protect my

00:21:33.760 --> 00:21:38.540
newly lightened skin and dispatched me to
the bazaar to buy bitter

00:21:38.540 --> 00:21:46.170
gourd, I used the money to rent an auto rickshaw.
